{"lastModified":1759237751758,"uri":"c::35404802089::vessel::d5cbfbde-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nYaretti 2210 is a comfortable motor yacht available for charter in Croatia. With 3 cabins and 6 berths, it can accommodate up to 6 people overnight. This makes “HAPPY 3” yacht the perfect choice for families or small groups of friends looking to explore the area.\n\nBoat equipment features Generator, Salon GPS plotter, BBQ, Bimini and Bow thruster. It also boasts Flat screen TV, Heating, Air conditioning, an Audio system and DVD Player. The fully-equipped galley includes Microwave, Ice maker, Freezer, Oven and Cooker.","blueprint":{"name":"HAPPY 3","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfbde-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::92d9cc00-5cd2-11f0-a46c-65f69164efd2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfbde-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::92c72e60-5cd2-11f0-b497-c5b6446664fd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfbde-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::92bca710-5cd2-11f0-a46b-65f69164efd2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfbde-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::92c4e470-5cd2-11f0-ba12-e1fd3ac9ba2f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfbde-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::92c42120-5cd2-11f0-b497-c5b6446664fd/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfbde-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::92bcf530-5cd2-11f0-a46a-65f69164efd2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfbde-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::92bdb880-5cd2-11f0-a46b-65f69164efd2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfbde-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::92bb6e90-5cd2-11f0-a46a-65f69164efd2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfbde-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::92c5ced0-5cd2-11f0-a46c-65f69164efd2/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cbfbde-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::92bd1